metadata.title: Jazwares Disney BB-8 Earbuds / In-Ear Headphones, Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens
features: Wherever you roll, take your music and a heroic droid with you! These Star Wars headphones feature comfy earbuds, each with a raised motif of BB-8 on the reverse
Moulded BB-8 artwork on each headphone
Compatible with all standard 3.5mm jack iPod, iPad and MP3 players
description: There is no need to travel to a galaxy far, far away to find the Star Wars Assorted Earbuds. Star Wars Earbuds use standard 3/8" jack and are compatible with iPhone, MP3 and DVD players. May the force of great sound be with you.
